# a simple naive saw synth to use in test patches

@ in note
@ in decay
@ in trig

@ out out

+ miditofreq mtf
> _in_@note mtf@in

+ phasor ph
> mtf@out ph@freq

# invert phase
+ sub iph
= 1 iph@in1
> ph@out iph@in2

# convert to audio range
+ map saw
= 0 saw@imin
= 1 saw@imax
= -1 saw@omin
= 1 saw@omax
> iph@out saw@in

+ segment env
= 1 env@val1
= 0 env@val2
> _in_@decay env@dur
> _in_@trig env@clock

+ mult vca
> saw@out vca@in1
> env@out vca@in2

> vca@out _out_@out

